items.desc:
The parameter to specify the geographic location in the format of countryCode|adminArea|locality. A countryCode is an ISO alpha-2 country code string. An adminArea is a state or the equivalent according to its associated country. A locality is a city or the equivalent according to its associated adminArea.
{
  "id": "US|CA|Cupertino",
  "entity": "locality",
  "displayName": "Cupertino, California, United States"
}
